#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:2
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Welcome to a quick aerial tour of Kennedy Space Center in Orbiter 2016!"
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:3
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Welcome to a quick aerial tour of Kennedy Space Center in Orbiter 2016!    This is a recorded flight, so just sit back and enjoy the view."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:5
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Accelerating down runway 33 of the Shuttle Landing Facility (SLF) in a DG type spaceplane."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:8
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Rotation and takeoff."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:10
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Gear up."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:12
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Orbiter now supports higher texture resolutions for improved realism."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:13
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Orbiter now supports higher texture resolutions for improved realism.    The area around KSC has been textured from aerial photographs with a resolution of about 1 meter per pixel."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:15
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "While the KSC terrain is flat, Orbiter's new surface elevation support has been put to use for modelling vegetation."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:16
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Buzzing the Vehicle Assembly Building (VAB)."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:18
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Orbiter 2016 also models water surfaces more realistically than previous editions."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:20
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Pad A of Launch Complex 39 (LC-39A) is ahead, used for launches of the Apollo program, and later the Space Shuttle."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:22
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "And there is LC-39B."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:23
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "And there is LC-39B.    Looks like a Shuttle is preparing for launch at this very moment."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:26
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "It's time to return to base. Preparing for landing."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:27
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Throttle to idle ..."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:28
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Throttle to idle ...    Gear down ..."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:30
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Coming in pretty high and fast."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:31
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "No need to panic ..."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:32
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "No need to panic just yet ..."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:35
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Smooth and easy"
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:36
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Touchdown!"
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:37
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "There you go - not exactly a regulation landing, but it is pretty hard to miss the SLF runway (it's one of the longest in the world)."
msgstr ""

#: Flights/3 Minute Tour of Kennedy Space Center/system.dat:38
msgctxt "Flight"
msgid "Thanks for watching - now it's over to you, commander."
msgstr ""

